Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.72,0:00:07.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The moment of vengeance is upon us!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.77,0:00:12.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The curtain will draw...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.73,0:00:19.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The masque of death is ready to commence!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.09,0:00:28.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A desperate crisis...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.80,0:00:30.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A splendid resurgence changes the solution to the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.06,0:00:32.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actors are frightening with their faces veiled...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.98,0:00:34.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All in this tragic masquerade!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.14,0:00:36.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.84,0:00:38.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.82,0:00:40.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.87,0:02:31.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Masques."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.41,0:02:36.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Basically, they were plays featuring masks before Shakespeare's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.62,0:02:38.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were a popular type of play in England until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.76,0:02:55.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The play that's being performed right now\Nis John Benson's "The Triumph of Folly."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.44,0:02:59.73,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,In Japanese, it would be, "Oroka sa no Shouri."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.23,0:02:59.73,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Shimizu Kinuko (26)\N{\fs12}Troupe Company Manager
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.82,0:03:10.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, this performance is really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.87,0:03:12.12,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,In order to achieve that effect...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:15.12,CharCard2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur3}Tabuchi Manabu (50)\NStage Art Director
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:15.12,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,We borrowed actual rapiers to practice with
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.66,0:03:54.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.28,0:03:55.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No script?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.58,0:03:57.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no call for a script.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.29,0:03:58.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a silent play.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.83,0:03:59.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.59,0:04:10.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He vanished!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.76,0:04:13.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a landing under the veranda.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.43,0:04:14.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He just has to jump down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.81,0:04:26.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, this scene is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.65,0:04:29.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a pivotal scene in which the king raises his cup in celebration...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.57,0:04:31.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Following the deaths of the prince and minister.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.99,0:04:36.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, it was the king who orchestrated the feud between the two.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:52.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The wine the king was just drinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.68,0:04:55.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was poisoned by the minister beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.69,0:05:14.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems like quite a bloody story.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.78,0:05:16.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The story is indeed an intricate one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.49,0:05:18.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This play has encountered a number of problems in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:20.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What you're saying is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.54,0:05:23.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They say that ever since the first performance in the 17th century...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.08,0:05:26.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This play has been cursed, and leads to the death of a cast member.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.43,0:05:37.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The guy playing the prince really looks like a prince, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.63,0:05:38.28,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.30,0:05:42.47,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,That is our star actor, by the name of Banno Robert.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.51,0:05:42.47,CharCard3,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Banno Robert (21)\N{\fs12}Stage Actor (Role of Prince)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.15,0:05:48.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Komazuka Hiroshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.15,0:05:50.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, you've heard of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.73,0:05:51.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.85,0:05:55.30,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Back when I was a student, I watched his movies all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.40,0:05:55.61,CharCard4,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Komazuka Hiroshi (50)\N{\fs12}Stage Actor (Role of King)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.20,0:06:00.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one playing the minister is Yabuki Atsushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.94,0:06:02.70,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,As for the lift I'm jumping on...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:05.80,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Think you could raise the platform a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.59,0:06:05.80,CharCard5,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Yabuki Atsushi (28)\N{\fs12}Stage Actor (Role of Minister)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.29,0:06:08.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In reality, during practice...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.08,0:06:10.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Suspicious happenings have come one after the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.38,0:06:12.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why we asked you, Detective Mouri...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.34,0:06:14.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.22,0:06:18.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It shall be as easy as relaxing on a boat—no, I mean, a cruise liner!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.53,0:06:39.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No problem at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:44.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There aren't any suspicious places, are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.29,0:06:48.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, where's the brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.04,0:06:51.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.46,0:06:54.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's such a big place, he could have gotten lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.80,0:06:55.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.22,0:06:58.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That kid is such a pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.31,0:07:14.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By switching this rapier with the real one...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.57,0:07:15.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Robert will...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.79,0:07:25.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kyoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.12,0:07:28.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although I may not know where you are now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.29,0:07:31.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I only hope you will see tomorrow's news.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.54,0:07:36.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because the news will be about the accidental\Ndeath of the man that's having a secret affair on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.84,0:07:40.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Robert...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.09,0:07:43.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come tomorrow, the sword of justice...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.64,0:07:46.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shall pierce right through your sinful heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.23,0:07:54.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.98,0:07:57.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.24,0:07:59.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.28,0:07:59.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.41,0:08:02.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.53,0:08:03.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're Detective Mouri's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.53,0:08:06.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me? I didn't hear a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.49,0:08:08.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no way you didn't hear anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.16,0:08:12.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you've heard, there's no way I can let you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.29,0:08:15.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until the show is finished, at the earliest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.72,0:08:26.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To be honest, staying here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.64,0:08:31.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.48,0:08:33.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My alcoholism is acting up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.47,0:09:03.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.01,0:09:05.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.30,0:09:08.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you seen a child about this tall?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.77,0:09:12.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haven't seen him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:13.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.64,0:09:15.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.86,0:09:23.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.25,0:09:33.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.00,0:09:36.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The real rapier is missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.21,0:09:38.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rapier?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.26,0:09:42.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.89,0:09:49.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.35,0:09:51.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it, I'm filing a complaint.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.56,0:09:53.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.64,0:09:54.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.85,0:09:58.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shocking him to death on the stage lift...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.73,0:10:00.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That doesn't sound like a bad idea either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.03,0:10:04.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It isn't like I was the one messing with the rapiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.61,0:10:06.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can still claim it was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.20,0:10:08.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, the problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.20,0:10:11.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do I switch roles before the real performance begins?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.74,0:10:13.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'll definitely take the bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.50,0:10:15.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, I'll talk him into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.71,0:10:19.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.00,0:10:21.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't have the money to pay me\Nback, so you're handing me your role?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.88,0:10:23.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.21,0:10:25.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's just no way for me to ready the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.80,0:10:27.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As such, I'm giving you my role.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.47,0:10:28.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.14,0:10:30.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The actual performance is soon, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.85,0:10:33.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:34.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a silent play.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.14,0:10:37.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since there's no script, it should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.94,0:10:38.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.98,0:10:39.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.31,0:10:41.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.36,0:10:44.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, hurry and tell the manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.69,0:10:47.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What if we kept it a surprise until we got on stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.24,0:10:51.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From an acting standpoint, I think it would be interesting to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.87,0:10:53.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.96,0:10:58.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.00,0:11:01.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll just leave this here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.97,0:11:09.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The trap I was going to remove...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.30,0:11:11.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:13.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So long as I fall to the side, I should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.18,0:11:17.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.11,0:11:25.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even an elephant can be poisoned to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.15,0:11:27.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That old man—he's about to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.49,0:11:32.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a gift from your fans?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.37,0:11:33.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.53,0:11:35.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, sake is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.83,0:11:42.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll accept it for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.92,0:11:47.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Komazuka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.17,0:11:48.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is everything going OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.47,0:11:49.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.43,0:11:50.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.05,0:11:54.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although Robert{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} and Yabuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} are\Ndoing well, these are their first starring roles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.35,0:11:57.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Komazuka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, please show them your guidance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.31,0:11:59.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.31,0:11:59.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.90,0:12:06.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just don't do anything foolish that would\Nembarrass me like you did during rehearsal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.82,0:12:07.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll pay closer attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.65,0:12:10.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Such a nice-sounding response...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.78,0:12:13.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Too bad you have zero acting talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.66,0:12:17.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not even sure how someone like you is allowed on the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.08,0:12:19.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Put this away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.87,0:12:22.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've stopped drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.29,0:12:24.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:27.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.17,0:12:28.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He just keeps going on and on and on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.01,0:12:31.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The main role was supposed to belong to me, originally.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:35.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But because of you, everything has been ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.26,0:12:39.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You must know by now that the audience is growing\Ntired of watching you only act like you've been poisoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.10,0:12:44.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, for the next performance, I'll be the one in the spotlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.99,0:12:53.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Everything will be just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.45,0:12:55.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I suppose, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.49,0:12:57.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.49,0:13:01.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've looked everywhere, but I can't find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.16,0:13:03.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be that something happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.25,0:13:04.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nah, no worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.83,0:13:06.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's always like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.01,0:13:14.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The moment of vengeance has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.89,0:13:19.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The curtain will draw...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:25.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The masque of death is ready to commence!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.47,0:14:03.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't have the slightest clue that this\Nperformance is about to become your last...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.73,0:14:10.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.44,0:14:11.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.57,0:14:16.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.61,0:14:18.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where has Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} gone off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.59,0:14:35.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did a guy like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.76,0:14:40.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said it, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.22,0:14:45.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"My dream is to see out the remainder of my life on the stage."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.30,0:14:49.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm merely obliging by fulfilling your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.27,0:14:54.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're almost to the climax.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.74,0:14:55.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.96,0:14:57.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems everything will work out without a hitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.49,0:15:06.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That Yabuki seems to really be into it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.08,0:15:10.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be that he performs better during showtime?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.54,0:15:14.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter, it'll be in this state that you put a sword right through him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.22,0:15:17.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't be showing mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.51,0:15:19.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whatever happens, don't blame me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.59,0:15:20.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's an accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.89,0:15:24.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The scene with those two looks completely different?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.89,0:15:25.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.14,0:15:27.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm just seeing things, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.56,0:15:32.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.08,0:15:49.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your pleas for mercy will be in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.63,0:15:59.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.59,0:16:00.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.59,0:16:01.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.34,0:16:02.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Robert is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.77,0:16:08.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.27,0:16:10.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it is just an accident, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.07,0:16:21.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that sound just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:26.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What goes around comes around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.54,0:16:35.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would be fantastic if this were actual wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.30,0:16:38.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just to be safe, I'll go have a look at the stage lift.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.69,0:16:58.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.73,0:16:59.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.57,0:16:59.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.21,0:17:12.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.67,0:17:13.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.29,0:17:14.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Call an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.34,0:17:17.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's too late...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.96,0:17:19.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The poison's already coursing through his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.67,0:17:23.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the punishment for making me look like a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.97,0:17:25.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, more importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.22,0:17:27.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who switched the rapier for a real one?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.76,0:17:29.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was the one who did...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:33.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's punishment for making my daughter suffer...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.64,0:17:34.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Robert...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.98,0:17:36.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.15,0:17:38.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Robert{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.36,0:17:45.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yabuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.95,0:17:47.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.66,0:17:50.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once I knew the rapier had been switched for a real one...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.08,0:17:51.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I decided to switch roles with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.75,0:17:54.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To repay the money I owed him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.83,0:17:56.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everything was going fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.58,0:18:01.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until I ended up falling into my own trap...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.84,0:18:03.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tabuchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.84,0:18:05.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry and shut off the power to the lift!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.97,0:18:06.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.85,0:18:09.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just what is going on here!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.43,0:18:12.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Robert{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:16.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am I going to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:19.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A shock that small won't kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.57,0:18:20.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still, we'll need an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.49,0:18:31.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, when was the rapier switched out?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.20,0:18:36.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The last time I checked, it was definitely the fake that was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.37,0:18:38.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is the fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.96,0:18:39.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.34,0:18:41.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course it's the fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.34,0:18:44.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was the one who secretly switched them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.55,0:18:45.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it wasn't just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.34,0:18:48.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To make it a poor conductor...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.26,0:18:50.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I also switched the wine inside the decanter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.85,0:18:53.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, at that point, I was really worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.19,0:19:02.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.69,0:19:07.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After escaping from the coffin...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.91,0:19:10.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I used the genuine rapier to cut the rope...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.03,0:19:11.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:13.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.16,0:19:17.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The real rapier is missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.71,0:19:24.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.34,0:19:25.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it, I'm going to file a complaint.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.76,0:19:29.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believed everything was all right at that point...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.05,0:19:29.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.84,0:19:30.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.76,0:19:33.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shocking him to death on the stage lift...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:36.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That doesn't sound like a bad idea either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.85,0:19:40.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It isn't like I was the one messing with the rapiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.27,0:19:42.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can still claim it was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.73,0:19:44.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be that even Robert{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.69,0:19:48.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In a rush to swap the rapier with the fake one being used in the play...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.53,0:19:52.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And to stop him from going to Yabuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s dressing room just in case...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.62,0:19:53.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The result was...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.87,0:19:57.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even an elephant can be poisoned to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.54,0:19:59.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That old man—he's about to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.17,0:20:03.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dealing with one criminal is relatively simple...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.17,0:20:05.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But three is too many to handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.55,0:20:07.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And even if they were stopped now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.30,0:20:08.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There will be a next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.84,0:20:09.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.55,0:20:15.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to save him, even though he's a criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.64,0:20:18.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll accept it for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.06,0:20:21.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Komazuka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.31,0:20:22.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is everything going OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.48,0:20:23.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.56,0:20:24.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.11,0:20:28.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although Robert{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} and Yabuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} are\Ndoing well, these are their first starring roles.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.61,0:20:31.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Komazuka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, please show them your guidance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.49,0:20:36.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, the show began.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.75,0:20:46.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A bottle cap should be enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.55,0:20:54.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, make Yabuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} lose consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.47,0:20:58.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next would Robert{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.90,0:21:04.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.15,0:21:11.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then, we have Komazuka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.38,0:21:35.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The evidence is all there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.43,0:21:37.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The three of them can't deny it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.56,0:21:41.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.52,0:21:45.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they would just realize the error of their ways\Nand not do something this mindless, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.52,0:21:49.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.11,0:21:50.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where were you this whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.11,0:21:52.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.20,0:21:54.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.45,0:21:55.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.57,0:21:56.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been looking everywhere for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.62,0:21:59.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.53,0:22:00.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'd better smarten up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.25,0:22:01.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.70,0:22:02.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.25,0:23:27.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You want to be in a masque, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.62,0:23:29.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you pull it off?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.63,0:23:33.43,Signs,,0,0,0,,STRANGE ATTEMPTED MURDER\NSCENARIO PLAYS OUT AT THE THEATER
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.00,0:23:30.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.17,0:23:33.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, let's give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.31,0:23:46.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That —is it supposed to be a masque?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.23,0:23:48.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.69,0:24:17.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.95,0:24:19.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ring Impression
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.98,0:24:24.97,Signs,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.17,0:24:22.78,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next time, Mom and Dad get along with one another!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.79,0:24:23.23,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.23,0:24:25.23,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Yes, really!
